-- Benin to Get $42.6 Million Water-Supply Project Loan From India
-- B y   S e r g e - D a v i d   Z o u e m e
-- 2013-05-30T13:27:30Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-30/benin-to-get-42-6-million-water-supply-project-loan-from-india.html
Benin  will receive a $42.6 million
loan from India for water-supply projects, Water Minister
Barthelemy Kassa said.  The loan has 20-year grace period with an annual interest
rate of 1.75 percent, Kassa told reporters in Cotonou, Benin.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Serge-David Zoueme in Porto Novo at 
 zsergedavid@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Randall Hackley at 
 rhackley@bloomberg.net  